== Pangabalangkas (Anatomy) ==

Mayayakit ya king dake nang babo kaili ning [[atian]] ing lapé ning [[tau]]. Atiyu king gulut ning [[dungus]], at lalam ne mu ning [[w:diaphragm (anatomy)|diaphragm]]. Kareng normal a tau, maki sukad ya iting manga 125&nbsp;× 75&nbsp;× 50 mm (5&nbsp;× 3&nbsp;× 2 [[pulgada]]), at maki bayat yang  150 gramo (5 [[ounce|oz]]).

Ing lapé ing pekamaragul nang [[w:organ (anatomy)|organu]]ng  ibat king [[mesenchyme]], at atyu iti king [[mesentery]]. Bibilugan de reng kumpul-kumpul a [[w:lymphoid]] [[w:biological tissue|tissue]] a itsurang malabinutil (granular), at mayayakit kareng mapinung sanga king sepu da reng [[w:vein|vein]] ampong [[w:artery|artery]]. Mituglung-tuglung la reng uyat a reti kareng mibayung (modified) [[capillary]] a ausan dang splenic sinus.   

Manga apulung porsientu (10%) kareng tau ing maki metung o maigit pang [[w:accessory spleen| lapéng panyaup]]. Maliari lang  mayakit deti malapit king [[w:hilum|hilum]] ning mismung lapé, ing salapaungan dalan nung nu la lulub at lulual king organu deng uyat ning lapé.

Ating mapilan a [[litid]] (ligament) ning [[w:peritoneum|peritoneum]] a tatalan king lapé<ref>{{NormanAnatomy|spleen}}</ref> (makasaup king pamanintindi king karelang lagiu nung isipan tamung ing "lien" metung yang [[w:root (linguistics)|katayang uyat]] para king "lapé")
* [[gastrolienal ligament]] (gastrosplenic) - ing mitutuglung king dungus ampo king lapé.
* [[lienorenal ligament]] (splenorenal) - ing mitutuglung king batu ampo king lapé.
* [[phrenicocolic ligament]] – ing mitutuglung king [[w:left colic flexure|kailing colic fixture]] ampo king [[w:thoracic diaphragm|thoracic diaphragm]].

Makatuglung ya king lapé ing libutad.

Mayayakit ya kareng dakeng binangal (cross section) ning lapé ing kilual a malutu ampong malambut, a mapipitna kareng aduang dakeng malambut a laman a makayagpang kareng aduang pekamaulagang diling papil ning lapé a mababanggit king lalam:<ref>{{BUHistology|07701loa}}</ref>

